title: Gingers Dreamworld (1985/VHSRip)
description: Starring: Bunny Bleu, Christy Canyon, Ginger Lynn, Lisa DeLeeuw, Loni Sanders, Laurie Smith, David Sanders, Greg Rome Two weeks ago, Michael Harris was your average everyday good-looking but modest med-student. Until his friend Harold gives him a gift. The next day, he awakens to a new roomate, a gorgeous sometimes (usually) mischievious blonde (Ginger) who is always coming up with new ways to please her master. Did Ginger learn her technique from the hedonist Zora, who derives her pleasures from a constant three ring sex circus, which includes two feline foxes, oral fixationists, and nymphomaniacs? Ginger finally finds her forte in the center ring with “all” holes filled. 1:26:54 https://www.imageuploads.co.uk/image/eTR10 https://www.imageuploads.co.uk/image/eTIW5 https://www.imageuploads.co.uk/image/eTalG
